item.title: 5.12.12 的 macOS 版本
item.description: 重要 FINAL VERSION, NO MORE UPDATES EVEN IF REQUESTED, BUILD ENVIRONMENT HAS BEEN DESTRUCTED 备注 SQLite(distributed with Qt) are built in the backage and have -plugin-sql-sqlite 备注 All builds have -no-openssl -securetransport. It means that we are using Secure Transport library of macOS to provide SSL connections. 备注 All builds have -no-icu because I think the ICU library is too big and, in most of the conditions, useless for common users.

item.title: 5.12.12 的 WebAssembly 版本
item.description: 重要 FINAL VERSION, NO MORE UPDATES EVEN IF REQUESTED, BUILD ENVIRONMENT HAS BEEN DESTRUCTED 备注 SQLite(distributed with Qt) are built in the backage and have -plugin-sql-sqlite 备注 All packages have -no-ssl because of compile failure with -ssl -openssl-linked. 备注 All builds have -no-icu because I think the ICU library is too big and, in most of the conditions, useless for common users. 备注 All builds are using emscripten SDK 1.
